snippet: Five people were injured in Philadelphia on Sunday when a car collided with a transit bus and flipped it on its side, according to transit officials and media reports....

headline.print_headline: Several Injured After Philadelphia Bus Flips on Side in Crash
headline.main: Several Injured After Philadelphia Bus Flips on Side in Crash

lead_paragraph: Five people were injured in Philadelphia on Sunday when a car collided with a transit bus and flipped it on its side, according to transit officials and media reports.
